img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee07f33dadb0c54323dc92cffdceedbc758914fa","tid":2092654,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T00:40:31.000Z","msg":"光復, 就是要恢復那些近年倒退的自由,人權,法治,被選舉權,教育制度,警隊風氣,政府文化,金融自主,街頭小店,遊客成份,中環寫字樓的租客成份,等等。<br />\n<br />\n革命,是要以突變方式,而不是漸變方式,去改變。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"39acda117c3132431ab3f86da3277c5550943117","tid":2092654,"uid":164477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"張圖可以做文宣"}}